Patch Set 1: Code-Review-2

The config and doc fixes are great, thanks for catching them.

I don't like messing with the DB migration script, though, especially since it's a minor typo.  So I'd prefer that you just leave the migration script as-is.  If you pull that file out of the patch, I'm +2 on this.

If you feel differently, this would be worth discussing at the Glance meeting.  Maybe I'm being too conservative here.
